    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ELEMENT_WAITING_DURATION

        public static final WaitingProperties ELEMENT_WAITING_DURATION
        Returns duration of the waiting for some web elements are present and suit some criteria. When "waiting.for.elements.time.unit" or "waiting.for.elements.time" are not defined then it returns 1 minute. Otherwise it returns defined duration value.

      • WAITING_ALERT_TIME_DURATION

        public static final WaitingProperties WAITING_ALERT_TIME_DURATION
        Returns duration of the waiting for appearance of an alert. When "waiting.alert.time.unit" or "waiting.alert.time" are not defined then it returns 1 minute. Otherwise it returns defined duration value.

      • WAITING_WINDOW_TIME_DURATION

        public static final WaitingProperties WAITING_WINDOW_TIME_DURATION
        Returns duration of the waiting for some window. When "waiting.window.time.unit" or "waiting.window..time" are not defined then it returns 1 minute. Otherwise it returns defined duration value.

      • WAITING_FRAME_SWITCHING_DURATION

        public static final WaitingProperties WAITING_FRAME_SWITCHING_DURATION
        Returns duration of the waiting for the switching to some frame succeeded. When "waiting.frame.switching.time.unit" or "waiting.frame.switching.time" are not defined then it returns 1 minute. Otherwise it returns defined duration value.

      • WAITING_FOR_PAGE_LOADED_DURATION

        public static final WaitingProperties WAITING_FOR_PAGE_LOADED_DURATION
        Returns duration of the waiting for waiting for a page is loaded. When "waiting.for.page.loaded.time.unit" or "waiting.for.page.loaded.time" are not defined then it returns 1 minute. Otherwise it returns defined duration value.
